page.title: 08Square 7
page.content:
The major land use of this square is{Intensively Managed Grassland}and {Deciduous Woodland.}The river flows through the square, but results in {Meadowland}only being a Minor land cover. There are five houses in this square, four of which are cottages and the other is a farm which employs several local people. The square also has a{Gas storage {Depot}in it.
{Attitudes { }All the residents of this square work on the land or for the estate, They know that future change is probable, but they would like life not to change.
